Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is completely falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it! Now is the time to\Nachieve honor! Take it all now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right!\N--We'll give vent to our fifty years of anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olminu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Yoichi. Extend the firing line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoichi! Nobunaga said,\N"Start shooting their rear. Break them."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musketmen! Keep reloading!\NDon't let your fuse extinguish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Toyo falls back, we provide cover fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since Toyo is Toyo,\Nhe probably won't fall back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we will also charge forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we keep this going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has the same smell as Kanegasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon the vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infantry, temporarily pull back.\NRearguard, spread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break down into smaller units.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disperse through narrow streets and make\Nyour way towards the Capitol Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the shock troopers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Shinsengumi will end them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.97,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 12\NStaring at Shinsengumi\N~The Song of the Fervid Kyushu Man~"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw! Withdraw! Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is falling back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with no rearguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, haven't we won this? We won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing of that retreat was too good.\NI have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Nobunaga! Lord Nobunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message from Yoichi on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has split into smaller squads and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has started spreading throughout the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are setting the houses ablaze\Nand obscuring our vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad... This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it... What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something is still off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are adapting far too quickly!\NNo way! Could the enemy leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...know about guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is coming... all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyo! Toyo! Nobunaga is calling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy... The enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all return to the main force.\NThis head is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shimazu cross...\NI will never forget that crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know of the Shimazu clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata Toshizou Yoshitoyo \Nof the Shinsengumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu Toyohisa, undersecretary to\Nthe Imperial Minister of the Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a warrior of the\NLand of the Rising Sun, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mere fact that you wear that crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mere fact that you are\Nof the Shimazu clan of Satsuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is more than enough reason to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must hold real resentment\Ntowards the Shimazu clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizakibaru, Mimikawa, Okitanawate,\NHetzugigawa, Sekigahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was it the Invasion of Korea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of so many possible reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by looking at you,\NI can tell you are not from my era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, I see. What have my\Ndescendants done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Shimazu. You will \Nnever be allowed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die. Do nothing but die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will never pardon you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebellious Satsuma,\Nyour death shall come to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Nobu?\NThe enemy is...! Nobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do...?\NShould we spread out, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The destructive power of muskets can\Nonly be fully brought out in a large unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, they are lacking in experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I break the force into squads,\Nno one will be qualified to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I send them all out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that will take too long,\Nand this castle town will be devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy, old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do berry smashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck has the old man\Nstarted to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know. He's just an old man.\NPlease let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, old fool?!\NI've had it with you, Lightning of Carthage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much easier to smash them all at once!\NThey taste better smashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoichi! Yoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a situation here, too.\NToyo... and the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu said to monitor the\Nenemy's movement from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look down upon the entire city!\NAre they rampaging on the streets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke... Are they randomly setting fires?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment. Please hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.77,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shake shake"\N"Creak creak"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The height of Elves sure comes in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Umm... Yoichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Abs... My abs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, the enemy forces are scattered\Nand moving in a disorderly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They appear to be chaotic at a glance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a method to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are making a detour,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are probably heading\Ntowards the Capital Building over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know their intention now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't given up the \Nplot to conquer this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their plan hasn't shifted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and won't be changed in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are persistent in executing their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone should leave the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Toyohisa up! Boobienue,\Ncome over here too, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map! Bring a map of this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy leader may be an\Nexpert in tactical maneuvering,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he is an amateur in strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that sounds a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Conquer the state"?\NThe Ends are saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of annihilation, \Nthey aim for conquest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that man was going\Nto take over Orte when he first appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the same Ends who seek\Nthe eradication of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing at the Northern Walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black King...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This idiot is smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu Toyohisa...\NWhat kind of path has he taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away, Shimazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plates... Foolish! Are you so desperate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't follow the way\Nof the warrior, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a war. There's no justification\Nfor taking the enemy's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no excuse we can make\Nto the enemy if we don't use
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every trick at hand to hammer out a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't listen to this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably not intentional,\Nbut Toyo is a genius
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to infuriating his enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the advantage of\Nthree frontline commanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That enemy took the bait that Toyo set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, he is too busy to command his troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy forces are advancing this way,\Nfaithfully following his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity for you, enemy leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the fool you've been\Nchasing around is only our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:13:03.84,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drip drip"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all set?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you are ready,\Nwe'll get out of here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we will let all the\Nenemy forces into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait in the surrounding\Nbuildings until they all enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At my signal, you'll all come out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olminu, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimated us.\NYou underestimated the Shinsengumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to mess around for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not once have I ever\Nunderestimated you, not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battlefield. I'll do\Nwhatever I gotta, even mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Elves! Fire arrows!\NRain fire down on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are barrels of oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The enemy is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... They die so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kill them so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...?! Ah... M-My charm was again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...used for dreadful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great feeling to box the enemy\Nin and fan the flames around them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be how that damn Mitsuhide\Nfelt watching Honnoji Temple burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu and Yoichi chose me as general,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never thought of myself that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all... above all,\NI am just an ambitious brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never be a warrior \Nlike my uncle or my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he is different...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oda Nobunaga, former Minister of the Right,\NDemon King of the Sixth Heaven, is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stake my life to buy time for Nobunaga\Nto turn the tide, he will definitely succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything for that to happen,\Nmessing around included.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many Shimazu troops died at Sekigahara,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those deaths became\Nthe foundation of our success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we die, we don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we can accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am to die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobunaga will turn my death into \Nthe foundation of our success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may take several ruthless steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shimazu attitude brought death to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detest this damn clan who die smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes are almost boasting,\N"We Shimazu are the only true samurai."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loathe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! Fire everything my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among all the people I have seen\Nfrom Satsuma, he is the greatest fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War is already madness from the outset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata, this is your moment to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I have not lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you still haven't lost.\NThis victory is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, beyond this, there is no victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the middle of a fight!\NWho the hell are you talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up your head, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dead bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a monster?! Die! Hurry up and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Just leave your head, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh... I can't even back him up\Nin such close combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw. That is my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back down here!\NIsn't the true battle just about to start?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I finally had the chance to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against a "samurai" from\Nthe Land of the Rising Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you for flying off like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back down, so I can take your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little while ago, weren't you the one\Nrunning from me and messing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind him. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would get to fight a "samurai"\Nfrom the Land of the Rising Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai... Samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeated... but victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyo! Hey, Toyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Lord, before my very eyes,\NI let your army...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet they didn't die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We obtained a great outcome\Nfrom this probing assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were also able to cripple\Nthe capital of Orte.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it is called a "test war"\Nin your country, right, Koreto?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice, his manner of speech...\NThere is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never forget or mistake it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobunaga... No wonder we couldn't\Nfind his remains at the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get to kill the idiot Nobunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Akechi Koreto Mitsuhide, \Nwill join your force.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
